text: Feldkirch is the second largest city in Vorarlberg. The largest hospital of Vorarlberg is there. About 33,000 people lived in Feldkirch, in 2019. Feldkirch has seven districts named Feldkirch, Tisis, Tosters, Nofels, Levis, Gisingen and Altenstadt. Category:Settlements in Vorarlberg Category:Cities in Austria
title: Feldkirch, Vorarlberg
